summary:
HELLO 


I work with conscious leaders to unlock their human super powers and make them a force for good. I combine powerful techniques from tantra, shadow work, and meditation to hyper charge personal transformation.

// WHY SHADOW WORK FOR CONSCIOUS LEADERS?
The positive impact of the companies we build are a direct representation of the level of awareness of it's leaders. Unconscious leaders make destructive companies. Conscious leaders can be an unimaginable force for good. My method to increase the level of awareness of leaders is 'Shadow Work'. In Shadow Work we will investigate what the hidden motives under your actions are. 

Are you an entrepreneur or leader in your field? Do you want to use your talents for good, and really feel you are contributing to the world? Let's talk.

// MY BACKGROUND
Over the last ten years I coached over 100 companies and individuals. Due to my background as Head of Growth of several tech startups like Peerby, Superbuddy and Vigga I am able to relate to the forces at play in the business world. 

// HOW I WORK
I run a 2 month intensive 1:1 program for conscious leaders. In this program we'll dive deep into you. We investigate why you are here on this planet, find out what the obstacles are to live your full potential and work step by step towards full a unlocking of your inner strength.
